data.description: This house is in a well established neighborhood and near two grade schools, a grocery store and other retail shops. It is a two-story house with 3,000 sq ft. of living space. Perfect for a large family with 5 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. The bathrooms and kitchen were remodled in 2019. Very spacious dining and living room with a quaint reading/relaxing area. Nice fenced in backyard and a two car garage with one entry off the alley.
